---
title: RefCell运行时借用状态机
---

stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Unused: 创建RefCell
    
    Unused --> Shared1: borrow()
    Unused --> Exclusive: borrow_mut()
    
    Shared1 --> Shared2: borrow()
    Shared2 --> Shared3: borrow()
    Shared3 --> SharedN: borrow()
    SharedN --> SharedN: borrow() [n+1]
    
    Shared1 --> Unused: drop(Ref)
    Shared2 --> Shared1: drop(Ref)
    Shared3 --> Shared2: drop(Ref)
    SharedN --> SharedNMinus1: drop(Ref) [n-1]
    
    Exclusive --> Unused: drop(RefMut)
    
    Shared1 --> Panic: borrow_mut()
    Shared2 --> Panic: borrow_mut()
    SharedN --> Panic: borrow_mut()
    Exclusive --> Panic: borrow()
    Exclusive --> Panic: borrow_mut()
    
    Panic --> [*]: 程序终止
    Unused --> [*]: RefCell离开作用域
    
    note right of Unused
        计数 = 0
        允许: borrow(), borrow_mut()
    end note
    
    note right of Shared1
        计数 = 1
        允许: borrow()
        禁止: borrow_mut() → panic
    end note
    
    note right of SharedN
        计数 = n
        多个共享借用共存
        所有都是不可变的
    end note
    
    note right of Exclusive
        计数 = -1
        独占可变访问
        禁止任何其他借用
    end note
    
    note right of Panic
        运行时panic
        "already mutably borrowed"
        或 "already immutably borrowed"
    end note
